    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just wish things could be easier for them. sometimes i think if i weren't here, they could finally just breathe and live their own lives without worrying about me all the time. do you think it's wrong to want to stop being a problem to solve? like, is there a way to do something good for them by just... stepping out of the way?",
